title: Episode 09 Ft. Sidney Starr
itunes:title: Episode 09 Ft. Sidney Starr
description:
Sidney Starr and Shauna Brooks join the ladies of Lip Service (Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire) and for the first time ever the ladies were at a loss for words as the celebrity transgenders discuss chicks with dicks, running trains, trap call, tucking and thottish behavior. Sidney Starr clears up the statement she allegedly made on mediatakeout about eating Tyga's booty like groceries, but calls some other people out.
